snippet.title: Phantom Rose 2 Sapphire - Steam Wishlist Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist it today on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1964200/Phantom_Rose_2_Sapphire

I’m building a roguelike game "Phantom Rose 2 Sapphire"! Putting my best effort to build the next, bigger iteration of Phantom Rose roguelike card game. 

Phantom Rose 2 features a new protagonist Aria, a new story, a new playable class, over 200 cards to collect, and lot more. I’ve been working very hard on it for the past year and it’s my goal to release it this year!

Game
Web: https://phantomrosegame.com
Twitter: https://twitter.com/phantomrosegame
Discord: https://discord.gg/phantomrose


Developer
Twitter: https://twitter.com/makaroll410
Instagram: https://instagram.com/makaroll410
